<h2 id="org23d05e7">Growth and inequality</h2>
<ul>
<li>In the cross section it does not appear the wealthier countries have lower inequality</li>
<li>We would like know how inequality evolves as countries develop</li>
<li>We don't have great data on this!</li>
<li>Piketty, Saez, Zucman (and others): World Wealth and Income Database</li>

</ul>
